@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080 
@firebaseToken = firebase_token_placeholder
@jobId = job_id_placeholder

### Firebase Auth check 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

### 작업 시작
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

{
  "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIHjXDxghqE",
  "title": "Interstellar Test"
}

### 상태 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status?job_id={{jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}

### 결과 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/result?job_id={{jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{firebaseToken}}